+# Implementation Summary
+
+## Files Modified
+
+- `packages/core/src/agents/agent-tool.ts`
+
+## Claims Applied
+
+### C1 — Centralize Agent Input Key Selection
+Extracted a module-level `resolveInputKey(schema)` helper (lines 33-43) that encapsulates the duplicated input-schema property inspection. Returns the single property name for one-property schemas, `'prompt'` for zero/multi-property schemas, and `undefined` when `properties` is absent or not an object. `AgentTool.mapParams` (line 118-121) and `DelegateInvocation.withUserHints` (line 230) now both call this helper instead of inlining the schema probing logic.
+
+### C2 — Reuse Hinted Child Invocation Construction
+Added `DelegateInvocation.buildHintedChildInvocation()` (lines 182-184) which composes `withUserHints` and `buildChildInvocation`. `shouldConfirmExecute` (line 189) and `execute` (line 196) now delegate to this single method instead of duplicating the two-step hinted-argument + child-invocation construction.
